description.narrative: In 2021, despite the several social crises and emergency situations, UNICEF Haiti has continued to support the government through its Ministry of Health and Population (MSPP) to strengthen the health system. Technical support was provided for the development of policy documents, standards, strategies and action plans, as well as for strengthening the management, quality and timeliness of data for better planning and evaluation of data. health interventions. The coordination of the response to the 2021 earthquake and COVID-19 has been strengthened. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:24/01/2022
